blog.name: yourluvmademecrazy
blog.title: 💫 I'm doing better than I ever was 💫
blog.description:
The names Jacqueline. I go by Jackie or Dude because that's what Taylor Swift called me when I met her on June 1st, 2018 in Chicago, Illinois.
Taylor followed 8/15/15 and liked 1x a photo of me and my best friend just chilling and a photo of me and the love of my life on New Years day and I haven't recovered since. She also told me she saw my tour outfits and thought I was really dedicated so she saved them and had someone come find me so she could meet me!!!!!
 Feeling 23 and blessed, living in a big ol' (windy) city.
follow my insta account @ YourQueenB
Taylor Swift enthusiast since 2008. Message me, let's be friends!
